snippet.title: Oorum Blood | Dude | Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju | @SaiAbhyankkar | Keerthiswaran | Mythri
snippet.description:
Presenting the Video song of 'Oorum Blood' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar Musical 
Song Title: 'Oorum Blood' (Tamil) 
Album: Dude (Tamil) 

Music Credits:

YOLO Rechords
Music Composed, Sung and Produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Lyrics: Paal Dabba 
Male Vocals: @SaiAbhyankkar 
Rap: Paal Dabba 
Female Vocals: Deepthi Suresh, Bhumi
Additional vocals: Kavitha Ilango, Surabhi Vimala, Lavanya Jayamohan, Gayathry Rajiv, D. Charumathi, Devu Mathew 
Vocal production - Jishnu Vijayan
Keys, Synths and Bass: @SaiAbhyankkar 
Classical Guitar - Keba Jeremiah
Flute: Nikhil ram 
Violin: Vignesh  
Electric & Acoustic Guitars: Robin sebastian  
Horns: Peter, John Kurvilla 
Music supervisor: Sachinlal  
Chorus Recorded at Sound Town Studios by Rajesh kannan 
Recorded at YOLO Rechords, Engineered by Rajesh Kannan  
Assistants: Sankeerth Shaji, Augustine Premkumar
Additional Programming by Rudh
Mixed by @SaiAbhyankkar  
Mastered by Rupendar Venkatesh at Sai 
Dhwani Studios

Listen to Oorum Blood song on your favourite streaming apps : https://bfan.link/oorum-blood-

Movie Credits:

Banner: Mythri Movie Makers
Writer & Director: Keerthiswaran
Producers: Naveen Yerneni, Y Ravi shankar
CO-Producer:  Anil Yerneni
Cinematographer: Niketh Bommi
Production Designer: Latha Naidu
Editor: Barath Vikraman
Choreographer: Anusha Viswanathan
Action: Yannick ben, Dinesh Subbarayan 
Costume Designer: Poornima Ramaswamy
Art Director: P.L. Subenthar
VFX Head & Supervisors: Ashok Mocharla, Nagu Talari 
DI: Mango post
Colorist: Suresh ravi 
Sound Design: Sync Cinema
Sound Mix: Tapas Nayak
Direction team: Krish Chidambaram, K.C. Perumal, Anirudh Ramesh, Tamilselvan Sankar, Karthick Sekar, Giriprasath, N. Nagaraj
Cinematography team: Yogi Chowdary kotapati, Govinda Rao.P, Dwarak Bharadwaj, Pradeep Raja
Editing Team: Lokesh Raj, Aathieswaran Rajakumar
Stills: M.Dinesh
Publicity Designer:  Viyaki
PRO: Suresh Chandra, Sathish S2Media
Title Animation: Sabari Ramiro
Production Controllers : Rangaraj Perumal, E. Suresh Nambiraj
Marketing: First Show

Lyrics:

Alaiye alaiye kaattula mazhaiye 
Allalley alla Dude
Sethara Pathara uduvan na
Othara Allalley alla Dude

Oorum Bloodu 
10000 Aura va kondu 
Achchadu
Nee ethanaiyo varuthangala paatha 
Athanaiyum worth nu thaan aakka

Dude’u unna minjinavan yaarum illa
Senjiru vachi
Just another person nu paathaa
ilichivan laa History ya kettaa

Mannan naa vanthana oor alara 
Kannan naa thottanna poo malara
Ennenenna solla Enna vella yaarum illa 
Raajathi Raajan naa
Raw’vaana

Unna thaana paathuka Naa inga kaathiruken 
Yen Nenji yengiruka

Una paakka vaanatha Thaandiyum vandhu 
en Kaadhala kaamipen naa naa naa

Yen moochavan Pechavan
Per solum azhagavan Yenakkula kalakkura 
Oxygen alavavan
Yaar Avan Yaar Avan 
Oor solum Star Avan 
Avan than Ennavanaa

Oru Alai Avan
Kalai Avan
Azhagiya Nilavavan
Nizalilum jolikkira
Niranthara oli avan
Sari avan
Thavaravan
Sirikira siripukku 
Avanthaan kaaranamaa

Mannan naa vanthanaa oor alara 
Kannan naa thottannaa poo malara
Ennenenna solla
Enna vella yaarum illa 
Raajathi Raajan naa
Raw’vaana Raavana

Thotta Dei Pattasa
naa vedikira 10000 wala hey!
Sutta Dei bullet ah
Naa therikira chal thu kon ye sala! 
I’m just chilling Aaya Cool ah!
Aya hooo! Proper style Ah 
Odra gaali
Naa podra velila la close Right ah Tight ah kudukuran pose

Mannan naa vanthana oor alara 
Kannan naa thottanna poo malara
Ennenenna solla
Enna vella yaarum illa 
Raajathi Raajan na
Raw’vaana Raavanaa

snippet.title: Mirai Trailer Telugu | Teja Sajja | Manchu Manoj | Karthik Gattamneni | PMF | 12th Sept
snippet.description:
Presenting the most awaited #MiraiTrailer Telugu!!

#Mirai is an upcoming Indian action-adventure film starring  #TejaSajja, #ManchuManoj, Ritika Nayak & Others. Directed by Karthik Gattamneni. Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory. 

In Cinemas 12th September, 2025 Worldwide.

Cast: Super Hero Teja Sajja, Manoj Manchu, Ritika Nayak, Shriya Saran, Jayaram, Jagapathi Babu

Crew: 
Director – Karthik Gattamneni
 Producers – T.G. Vishwa Prasad, Krithi Prasad

Tere dil pe haq mera hai
Tu sanam beshaq mera
Phir lakeerein hon ya na ho
Tu mera hai tu mera hai

Jo tu aag hai
Haan to phir mujhe
Jalne ka shauk hai
Jalne ka shauk hai
Marne se kahin
Jyada haan tujhe
Khone ka khauf hai
Khone ka khauf hai

Tu chahiye mujhe
Chahe kahe ise 
Mera junoon ya phir 
Tu zid meri


Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe likh chuka hoon
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi ki
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai 
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera


Paane ki tujhko
Hasrat liye hi
Raaton ko main
Jagta hoon
Kyu jaane phir bhi
Dushaman teri do
Ankhon ko 
Main lagta hoon
Kahe na chahe tu mujhe
Karunga tujhe ishq main
Mujhe ye parwaah nahi 
Jo bhi ho mera anjaam har haal mein
Tu chahiye mujhe
Jo bhi saza mile 
Parwaah hai phir kise
Anjaam ki 
Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe 
Likh chuka hu
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera

snippet.title: Do You Wanna Partner - Official Trailer | Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Do You Wanna Partner Official Trailer
Starring Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty, Jaaved Jaaferi, Nakuul Mehta, Neeraj Kabi, Shweta Tiwari, Sufi Motiwala, Rannjivay Singha, Lokesh Mittal, Indranil Sengupta, Ayesha Raza
Directed by Archit Kumar and Collin D'Cunha
Written by Nandini Gupta, Aarsh Vora and Mithun Gangopadhyay
Created by Mithun Gangopadhyay and Nishant Nayak
A Dharmatic Entertainment Production

Official Release Date September 12, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Best friends Shikha and Anahita turn entrepreneurs with an exciting craft beer brand, Jugaaro, to stand out in the crowded NCR beer market. However, they face gender discrimination every step of the way. To fight for an equal place in this male dominated sector, they decide to invent a fictitious male partner to help smooth their way. Invariably, things don’t go exactly as planned. What follows are their collective adventures & misadventures in trying to build a successful start-up amidst the current boom, as the bunch of misfits band together and become a family.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

Sunderkand, Sunderkand chaupai, sunderkand path, sunderkand full, sunderkand in hindi, सम्पूर्ण सुन्दरकाण्ड पाठ, Sampurn SunderKand, sunder kand, sunderkand ka path, sangeetmay sunderkand, sunderkand ramayan, Sunderkand fast, Sunderkand with lyrics, Sunder kand By Prem Parkash Dubey, Sunderkand live, Mangalwar Special, Kam samay main sunderkand, 45 min mein sunderkand, sunderkand in hindi, हनुमान जी का सुंदरकांड, रामायण का सुंदरकांड, संपूर्ण सुंदरकांड चौपाई, सुंदरकांड हिंदी में,सुंदरकांड डाउनलोड, Mangalwar special sunderkand, Tuesday special sunderkand, Tuesday speical, Sunderkand ka path kese karein, अब तक का सबसे कम समय मे गाया गया सम्पूर्ण सुन्दरकाण्ड पाठ, Sunderkand ki chaupaiya, sunderkand sunne ke labh,

snippet.title: Madharaasi - Official Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | Vidyut | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil drops the much-awaited official trailer of Madharaasi, an action-packed emotional drama written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Starring Sivakarthikeyan in a bold, intense role alongside the talented Rukmini Vasanth, the trailer gives a powerful glimpse into a gripping narrative filled with high-stakes moments, strong character arcs, and impactful storytelling. Backed by a compelling background score from Anirudh Ravichander, Madharaasi promises to be a high-voltage entertainer that blends mass appeal with emotional depth.

With stunning visuals, hard-hitting dialogues, and a riveting plot, the Madharaasi trailer has already begun trending among fans of Tamil action movies, Sivakarthikeyan's latest films, and AR Murugadoss' direction. Whether you're here for the sharp screenplay, Anirudh’s electrifying music, or the powerful screen presence of the leads, this is one film that’s gearing up to be a Tamil cinema blockbuster in 2025. Don’t miss out—watch the trailer now and be part of the growing excitement around #MadharaasiTrailer.

#Madharaasi Grand release worldwide on September 5th ❤‍🔥

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic - Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
Before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen, together. 

When a lost prince is rescued and raised in exile, he grows up unaware of his past. Years later, he returns to uncover the truth about his father’s murder and his mother’s imprisonment, and must rise to reclaim his place as the rightful king.

Baahubali: The Epic will be released in theaters across the U.S. October 31st.

#IGN #Movies

About Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle:
Tanjiro Kamado – a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon. 

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps’ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.
The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons’ stronghold – the Infinity Castle. 

And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

snippet.title: गणेश चतुर्थी Special |नॉनस्टॉप गणेश भजन Nonstop Ganesh Bhajan |Ganesh Song | Ganesh Chaturthi Bhajan
snippet.description:
गणेश चतुर्थी Special |नॉनस्टॉप गणेश भजन Nonstop Ganesh Bhajan |Ganesh Song | Ganesh Chaturthi Bhajan


तो आईए आज पावन हृदय से इस भजन द्वारा जो मांगना है मांग लीजिए।
श्याम बाबा सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण करें। 🙏

गणेश जी के रोज नए नए भजन सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़ें रहे व् नए नए भजनों का आनंद उठाये भजन पसंद आये तो कमेंट में '' जय श्री गणेश " जरुर लिखें || Jai Shree Shyam 🌹🌹

⭐Song : 
मेरे घर भी पधारो देवा
गौरी नंदन थारो अभिनंदन 
जल्दी से आओ गणपत
सबसे पहले तुम्हे मनाऊं 
मेरे लाडले गणेश प्यारे प्यारे
तस्वीर तुम्हारी है
मेरे कीर्तन में रंग बरसाओ 
बल बुद्धि के दाता 
श्री गणेश जी के 108 नाम
सुखकर्ता दुःखहर्ता आरती
⭐Singer : 
⭐Lyrics : Traditional
⭐Music: Binny Narang (9991980610)
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma (7015960610)
⭐Label Bhakti Sadhna (9466651081)
⭐Category: Hindi Devotional (Shyam Bhajan)
भक्ति साधना कंपनी से भजन बनवाने के लिए और भजन रिलीज़ करवाने के लिए संपर्क करे 9466651081

snippet.description:
𝐀𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐎 𝐂𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐒 :

𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆 𝐍𝐀𝐌𝐄 : 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓

𝐋𝐘𝐑𝐈𝐂𝐒 & 𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂 & 𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐀 𝐑𝐀𝐉𝐔 ~ {𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐦𝐮𝐫𝐮}

𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑'𝐒  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐑𝐀𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐀

𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐍𝐒 : 𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐤𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐡 𝐊𝐞𝐲𝐛𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝
                    𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐬𝐚𝐝 : 𝐓𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐚 & 𝐃𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐚𝐤
                     𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐮 :𝐓𝐚𝐩𝐞𝐬
                     𝐒𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐡 : 𝐑𝐡𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐦 𝐏𝐚𝐝𝐬
                    𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐬 : 𝐅𝐥𝐮𝐭𝐞

 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐃𝐔𝐂𝐄𝐑 : 𝐓𝐍,𝐘𝐄𝐋𝐋𝐀 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜 𝐋𝐚𝐛𝐞𝐥 : 𝐓𝐍𝐘𝐑 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜

𝐒𝐏𝐄𝐂𝐀𝐋 𝐓𝐇𝐀𝐍𝐊𝐒 : 𝐘𝐀𝐃𝐈 𝐌𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐑𝐀𝐉 & 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

𝐒𝐔𝐁𝐒𝐂𝐑𝐈𝐁𝐄 𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐌𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐓𝐍𝐘𝐑 𝐅𝐎𝐋𝐊 𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆𝐒 : https://www.youtube.com/@UC-WbBqf1caicfX24tao0HLw 

𝐒𝐔𝐁𝐒𝐂𝐑𝐈𝐁𝐄 𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐌𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐕𝐌𝐂 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐎𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍𝐀𝐋 𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆𝐒 : https://www.youtube.com/@VMCDEVOTIONAL

𝐒𝐔𝐁𝐒𝐂𝐑𝐈𝐁𝐄 𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐌𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐎𝐌 𝐁𝐇𝐀𝐊𝐓𝐇𝐈 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐋𝐔 : https://www.youtube.com/@OmBhakthiPatalu-b8u

en-IN.title: 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 | 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 | 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐡 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐢 𝐒𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 | 𝐕𝐦𝐜 𝐃𝐞𝐯𝐨𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐚𝐥
en-IN.description:
𝐀𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐎 𝐂𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐒 :

𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆 𝐍𝐀𝐌𝐄 : 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓

𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑'𝐒  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐑𝐀𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐀

                    𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐬𝐚𝐝 : 𝐓𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐚 & 𝐃𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐚𝐤

                     𝐒𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐡 : 𝐑𝐡𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐦 𝐏𝐚𝐝𝐬
                    𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐬 : 𝐅𝐥𝐮𝐭𝐞

 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐃𝐔𝐂𝐄𝐑 : 𝐓𝐍,𝐘𝐄𝐋𝐋𝐀 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

snippet.title: Mangli Sitapathi Ramchandra | Full Song | Kabir Das Bhajan | Indravathi Chauhan | Suresh Bobbili
snippet.description:
🌸🙏 Sitapathi Ramchandra Bhajan | Full Song 🙏🌸
A soulful devotional offering sung by Mangli and Indravathi Chauhan, composed by Suresh Bobbili, with the divine words of Kabir Das Ji. This bhajan celebrates the glory of Lord Sri Rama and fills the heart with peace, devotion, and bhakti.
✨ May Lord Ram’s blessings bring love, light, and positivity into your life.
🔔 Stay connected with us for more soulful bhakti songs and spiritual music.

#Mangli #IndravathiChauhan #SureshBobbili #KabirDas #RamBhajan #SitapathiRamchandra #BhaktiSong #DevotionalSongs #RamBhakti 

This Song is an Adaptation of Sant Kabir Das Ji’s Bhajan

Music - Suresh Bobbili

DOP - Tirupathi

gu.title: 🌸 નોનસ્ટોપ ગણેશ ભજનો🌼 ગણેશ ચતુર્થી સ્પેશિયલ ગીતો🎶ટોચના 10 ગણેશ ભજનો
gu.description:
આ ભાવપૂર્ણ ગણેશ ચતુર્થી સ્પેશિયલ ભજન પ્લેલિસ્ટ સાથે ભગવાન ગણેશના દિવ્ય આશીર્વાદની ઉજવણી કરો 🎶🐘. આ શક્તિશાળી ગણેશ ભજન, આરતીઓ અને મંત્રો જીવનમાંથી શાંતિ, સકારાત્મકતા, સમૃદ્ધિ લાવે છે અને તમામ અવરોધો દૂર કરે છે 🌸💫.

🌼 પ્લેલિસ્ટમાં શામેલ છે:
1️⃣ જયદેવ જયદેવ જય મંગલ મૂર્તિ
2️⃣ જય ગણેશ જય ગણેશ દેવા
3️⃣ સુખ કર્તા દુઃખ હરતા આરતી
4️⃣ ગણેશ મંત્ર – ઓમ ગણ ગણપતયે નમો નમઃ
૫️⃣ ગણેશ બીજ જાપ
6️⃣ ગણેશ ગાયત્રી મંત્ર
૭️⃣ ગણેશ ચાલીસા
૮️⃣ ગણેશ પંચરત્નમ
9️⃣ ગણપતિ અથર્વશીર્ષ
🔟 બંધુ યેઇલ માહેરી

🌸✨ ગણેશ ભજન સાંભળવાના ફાયદા:
🪔 જીવનમાંથી અવરોધો દૂર કરે છે
🪔 શાંતિ, સમૃદ્ધિ અને સફળતા લાવે છે
🪔 ઘરને સકારાત્મકતા અને દૈવી ઉર્જાથી ભરી દે છે
🪔 ગણેશ ચતુર્થીની ઉજવણી દરમિયાન શ્રદ્ધા મજબૂત કરે છે

🕉️🙏 ચાલો આ ગણેશ ચતુર્થીએ ભગવાન ગણેશની સ્તુતિ કરીને જીવનમાં સુખ, સમૃદ્ધિ અને શાંતિનું સ્વાગત કરીએ. 🌼✨

ગાયક - મનોજ ઠાકુર

સંગીતકાર - અવિજિત દાસ

snippet.title: Nesthama Iddari Telugu Lyrical Song l Pelli Pandiri l Jagapathi Babu, Raasi | S P Balu, K S Chithra
snippet.description:
Listen & Enjoy Nesthama Iddari Song with Telugu Lyrics from the Movie Pelli Pandiri, Starring Jagapathi Babu & Raasi. A Beautiful Melody Sung by S. P. Balasubrahmanyam & K. S. Chithra, with Music by Vandemataram Srinivas and Directed by Kodi Ramakrishna.

Song Details:

Song Name: Nesthama Iddari 
Singers: S. P. Balasubrahmanyam, K. S. Chithra
Lyrics: Guru Charan
Music: Vandemataram Srinivas

Movie Details:

Movie Name: Pelli Pandiri
Banner: S R S Art Movies
Producers: M.C. Sekhar, Ramesh Babu
Director: Kodi Ramakrishna
Starring: Jagapathi Babu, Raasi

Nesthama Iddari Song Telugu Lyrics:

నేస్తమా ఇద్దరి లోకం ఒకటేలేవమ్మా
అందుకే నా కన్నులతో లోకం చూడమ్మా
ఈ గుండెలోన నీ ఊపిరుంటే
ఈ కళ్ళలోన నీ కలలు ఉంటే
ఊహల రెక్కల పైన ఊరేగే దారులు ఒకటే
చూపులు ఎవరివైనా చూపించే లోకం ఒకటే 
బుగ్గ మీద వెచ్చని సిగ్గు వచ్చినప్పుడు దానిని అడుగు
ఎర్రదనం అంటే చెబుతుందీ
పెదవి కొమ్మ పూసిన పువ్వు అందమైన నీ చిరునవ్వు
తెల్లరంగు అట్టా ఉంటుందీ
నీలో నిలువున పులకలు రేగిన వేళా
నువ్వే పచ్చని పైరువు అవుతావమ్మా
దిగులు రంగే హ హ నలుపు అనుకో హ హ
ప్రేమ పొంగే హ హ పసుపు అనుకో హ
భావాలను గమనిస్తుంటే ప్రతి రంగును చూస్తున్నట్టే
చూపులు ఎవరివైనా చూపించే లోకం ఒకటే
మొదటిసారి నీ గుండెలలో తీయనైన ఆశలు రేపి ఆ కదలికే ఉదయం అనుకోమ్మా
చూడలేని ఆవేదనతో కలత చెంది అలిశావంటే సాయంత్రం అయినట్టేనమ్మా
నీలో నవ్వినా ఆశలు నా చెలివైతే నేనై
పలికిన పలుకులు నీ కూలుకైతే
ఇలవు నీవే హ హ రవిని నేనై హ హ
కలువ నీవే హ హ శశిని నేనే హ
ఒక్కరి కోసం ఒకరం అనుకుంటూ జీవిస్తుంటే
చూపులు ఎవరివైనా చూపించే లోకం ఒకటే

snippet.title: Onbathu Kolum & Vinayagar Songs | ஒன்பது கோளும் & சிறந்த விநாயகர் பாடல்கள் | Vinayaka Chaturthi 2025
snippet.description:
🙏✨ விநாயக சதுர்த்தி 2025 சிறப்பாகக் கொண்டாட, இனிய விநாயகர் பக்திப் பாடல்கள் தொகுப்பு இங்கே. இந்த ஜூக் பாக்ஸில் ஒன்பது கோளும், ஓங்காரமே, மூன்று தமிழ், புனிதம் புனிதம், அருகம்புல்லில், நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன், மற்றும் ஜெய கணேசா போன்ற பிரபலமான பாடல்கள் இடம்பெற்றுள்ளன. பூஜை, விழா மற்றும் பக்தி நேரங்களுக்கு சிறந்த தொகுப்பு.

🎶 பாடல்கள் மற்றும் நேரங்கள்:
00:00 – ஒன்பது கோளும் | Onbathu Kolum
13:07 – ஓங்காரமே | Ongarame
17:49 – மூன்று தமிழ் வாங்க | Moondru Thamizh
23:07 – புனிதம் அரசமரம் | Punitham Punitham
27:36 – அருகம்புல்லில் இருப்பது யாரு | Arugampullil
47:40 – நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன் | Nettriyile Kuttikkonden
52:58 – ஜெய கணேச பாஹிமாம் | Jaya Ganesa

🌺 இந்த சதுர்த்தியில் விநாயகர் அருள் உங்கள் குடும்பத்திற்கு மகிழ்ச்சி, ஆரோக்கியம் மற்றும் செழிப்பை வழங்கட்டும்.
👉 மேலும் பல பக்திப் பாடல்களுக்காக Like, Share, Subscribe செய்யுங்கள்.

🙏✨ Celebrate Vinayaka Chaturthi 2025 with a divine collection of powerful Ganesha devotional songs. This special jukebox features evergreen Tamil Vinayagar songs including Onbathu Kolum, Ongarame, Moondru Thamizh, Punitham Punitham, Arugampullil, Nettriyile Kuttikkonden, and Jaya Ganesa. Perfect for Pooja, Festive Celebrations, and Bhakti moments.

🎶 Songs in this Jukebox with Timings:
0:00 – Onbathu Kolum | ஒன்பது கோளும்
13:07 – Ongarame | ஓங்காரமே
17:49 – Moondru Thamizh | மூன்று தமிழ் வாங்க
23:07 – Punitham Punitham | புனிதம் அரசமரம்
27:36 – Arugampullil | அருகம்புல்லில் இருப்பது யாரு
47:40 – Nettriyile Kuttikkonden | நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன்
52:58 – Jaya Ganesa | ஜெய கணேச பாஹிமாம்

🌺 May Lord Vinayaka bless you and your family with happiness, health, and prosperity this Chaturthi.
👉 Don’t forget to Like, Share & Subscribe for more devotional songs.
